episodes.title: The horrific cult tragedy that occurred during Y2K
episodes.description:
Kanungu is the town in Uganda where this infamous doomsday cult was born, and ended with horrific deaths that still haunt many people in the country to this day.
Feel free to correct any information I got wrong.
